## Context

* We use TailwindCSS with Shadcn/UI to add style in our application.

## Rules

* AVOID `space-y-{number}` or `space-x-{number}` and try to always use `flex` with gap
* AVOID using `bg-opacity-{number}` and use instead `bg-color-value/{number}`